descr: "Significant health events and conditions for a person related to the patient relevant in the context of care for the patient."

fields.name: code
fields.descr: "The actual condition specified. Could be a coded condition (like MI or Diabetes) or a less specific string like 'cancer' depending on how much is known about the condition and the capabilities of the creating system."

fields.name: outcome
fields.descr: "Indicates what happened as a result of this condition.  If the condition resulted in death, deceased date is captured on the relation."

fields.name: onsetAge
fields.descr: "Either the age of onset, range of approximate age or descriptive string can be recorded.  For conditions with multiple occurrences, this describes the first known occurrence."

fields.name: onsetRange
fields.descr: "Either the age of onset, range of approximate age or descriptive string can be recorded.  For conditions with multiple occurrences, this describes the first known occurrence."

fields.name: onsetPeriod
fields.descr: "Either the age of onset, range of approximate age or descriptive string can be recorded.  For conditions with multiple occurrences, this describes the first known occurrence."

fields.name: onsetString
fields.descr: "Either the age of onset, range of approximate age or descriptive string can be recorded.  For conditions with multiple occurrences, this describes the first known occurrence."

fields.name: note
fields.descr: "An area where general notes can be placed about this specific condition."
